Package: producer.pkg
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Package Trait Dispatch Producer Example
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mossa Merhi", "Reimert", , "mossa@struchstrup.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Eleanor", "Andersson", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Demonstrates miniextendr's cross-package trait dispatch capabilities.
    Defines the Counter trait and implements it for SimpleCounter. Objects created
    here can be passed to consumer.pkg functions that operate on the Counter trait
    interface, proving ABI compatibility via type tag matching.
